			<h4 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">House Rules</h4>		
			<ul class="unstyled">
				<li>If there is a "push" (tie) for one of the bets in a parlay, then that bet is simply removed from the parlay and the payout is recalculated.<hr></li>
				<li>A maximum of eight bets are allowed in a parlay.<hr></li>
				<li>You cannot parlay the moneyline and the spread on the same game. You also cannot parlay the over and the under on the same game, duh.<hr></li>
				<li>Bets using the point spread and bets on the over/under are paid at 11/10. In other words, you must bet 11 to win 10.<hr></li>
				<li>Parlays are paid out according to their true odds.<hr></li> 
				<li>All bets are final.</li>
			</ul>
